text.section:
The Secretary of State shall cancel the participation of a Program participant if:
the Program participant fails to notify the Secretary of State of any legal name change or change in address or telephone number in the manner required by § 4-524 of this part;
the Program participant files a request for withdrawal of participation under § 4-522(c)(2) of this part;
the Program participant submits false information in applying for participation in the Program in violation of § 4-523 of this part; or
the Secretary of State forwards mail to the Program participant and the mail is returned as undeliverable.
